<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Unable to Verify</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body, html {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            height: 100%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #ff7e5f, #feb47b); /* Soft gradient background */
            color: #ffffff; /* White text for better contrast */
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7); /* Semi-transparent black background */
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        h1 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        a {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #ff7e5f;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        a:hover {
            background-color: #feb47b;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Unable To Verify</h1>
        <p>The link has expired or is invalid. Please request a new verification link.</p>
        <p>Please Try Again Later </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

